Question: Given two non-negative integers low and high. Return the count of odd numbers between low and high

Solution:

class Solution {
    public int countOdds(int low, int high) {
        int num=high-low+1;  //counting total numbers in range
 
		if(low%2!=0 && high%2!=0)  
            return num/2 + 1;
        
        else
		return num/2;
    }
}
